As I was only there for one night I didn't utility all the services the hotel had to offer.	A few weeks ago I visited this beautiful hotel and I stayed only one night because I was taking a cruise.	We got there on Thursday night and didn't have to stand in any lines to check in.	We didn't stay there long, it was basically a place to sleep for the night so considering that I thought the $210 for the room & $28 for the parking was VERY high but I really had no complaints about the hotel or the staff.